settings.description: Idk what to do anymore but while I think, take this level,enjoy.
I know that I said the 1-8 was the final level of the first world but I exceeded and finally I create THIS,is a a """"""short"""""" level,enjoy.
We finish the first world,the next one is in the desert.
The next level is the larry's castle,enjoy.
First time I put the raccoon tail power up,enjoy.
The first fortress.I don't have anymore to say.
I think I'm getting better at making levels.
In this cave are only jumping enemies (except the spike tops) enjoy.
The start from a weird adventure (I speak spanish but i'm trying to speak english).

so much sand, with so many coins found deep under such! think you can unearth enough for a nice three extra lives?
don't forget to check what's in the bricks as well!
seems this normal ol wooden plains level got flooded by something! best to watch out for the flopping fish, for they can still harm you!
Esquiva la balas y no te resvales en el hielo, buena suerte.
waterfalls, koopas, ptooies, and a incredible view of a nice sunset! what more can you ask for minus a hidden hammer suit?~

Caves... filled with bats and moles! don't forget the iconic buzzy beetles as well!

shame there's no cave ceiling tiles though.
Careful, these creepy crawling beetles just love roaming around on all these wooden walkways! think you can find their hidden Tanooki suit though?
Wiggler ahoy! seems these caterpillars and butterflies are all around this chilly place!
